getMerchants

public DataLoader getMerchants(double latitude,
                               double longitude,
                               java.lang.String postCode,
                               java.lang.String countryCode,
                               java.lang.String language,
                               DataLoadListener listener)
Description copied from interface: TBRestaurantsDAO
Returns all the restaurants for the location provided postCode is not necessary but if postCode is provided , it has first priority than location. countryCode and language are optional. If not provided then NL will be used for both.

Specified by:
getMerchants in interface TBRestaurantsDAO
Parameters:
latitude - double with the location of merchants to retrieve
longitude - double with the location of merchants to retrieve
postCode - String with the postcode of merchants to retrieve
countryCode - String with the country code of merchants to retrieve
language - String with a search term to use in merchant filtering
Returns:
DataLoader object performing a network operation. When returned, it allows the external developer to cancel it in case the app does not need the data anymore
